							<h1>
								<a href="http://finansday.com/informatsiya-o-vkladah-dlya-novichka.html" title="">Информация о вкладах для новичка</a>
							</h1>
							<div class="comment-bubble">
								<a href="http://finansday.com/informatsiya-o-vkladah-dlya-novichka.html#addFeedback" title="Комметарии к записи">0</a>
							</div>
							<div class="article_info pull-left">
								<span>От </span>
								<a href="http://finansday.com/author/finday" title="Записи finday" rel="author">finday</a>								<span class="vert_sep">|</span>
